## 9) Current UX flows (what works now)

### 9.1 Build/Upgrade structure

* Structures tab shows each structure card:

  * locked vs level
  * worker requirement
  * build/upgrade cost display
  * Build/Upgrade button checks aggregated inventories

### 9.2 Manage structure

* “Manage” opens structure-specific controls:

  * assign/remove workers
  * farm crop selection + start/stop logic
  * pump/reservoir status
  * (future) radio/stable remote options

### 9.3 Citizens tab

* Shows all settlement citizens
* Shows assignment at a glance
* Allows:

  * remove from duty
  * return to caravan (crew cap permitting)
  * release

### 9.4 Settlement storage tab

* Shows inventory dropdown

  * caravan storage
  * each built structure’s local storage
* Allows transfer between any local inventories + caravan

